The '''French destroyer ''Opiniâtre''''' was one of four {{sclass-|Aventurier|destroyer}}s that was built for the [[Argentine Navy]] in the early 1910s. All four ships were taken over by the French Navy after the start of the [[First World War]] in August 1914.

